## Modern Restoration Additions (2025)

**Files**: Modern build system (CMakeLists.txt), documentation, packaging

**Copyright**: This restoration work is released under the same terms as the original to maintain maximum compatibility and preserve the public domain / permissive nature of the original codebase.

**Modern Additions Include**:
- K&R to ANSI C function signature conversions
- Modern build system (CMake)
- Cross-platform compatibility enhancements
- Documentation and educational materials
- Packaging and distribution configuration

**Philosophy**: All modern additions maintain the authentic 1984 gameplay experience while ensuring compatibility with contemporary systems. No modern game mechanics have been added.

